description:
Users require lots of different tools and stuff in order to work effectively, such as
- Smartphone
- Selfie Sticks or smartphone stands
- Pens
- Trashcan
- Bottles
- Glasses
- Ashtray
- Pencil Sharpener
- Fidgets
- Airpod case
- Headphones
- Toothpick
- Keychain


This way the desk tends to become crowded and messy and people start shifting things around.
